{"tid":1374140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每人罰抄十次： 我以後唔會再叫前線撤退","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T19:21:57.000Z","uid":225737,"like":103,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd9b714e536a18520ce7bae06f9285c9cb32031","tid":1374140,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"見到前線巴打一句<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我地想講既係，做得前線，俾人拉，俾人打，預撚左啦。</code></pre><br />\n好心酸<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔需要我地擔心佢安危，只需要我地一句支持，甚至唔反對，已經足夠。<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，我地以後唔會再叫你做乜做乜。<br />\n<br />\n每人罰抄十次：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n我以後唔會再叫前線撤退<br />\n</span></span><br />\n（真係打咗十次冇 copy and paste <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"3833116601f20e4474ed9b91d024c0a35357f925","tid":1374140,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:23:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1aab3d0a0994cf7b88cd5b65cbe04e618550e37a","tid":1374140,"uid":225737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:24:10.000Z","msg":"聽日遮打見"},{"pid":"d68fa03ce2d15ee03eeb687c5f132f29a5e088bb","tid":1374140,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88d4cd36a21847cf980b7477939442378cca065","tid":1374140,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37f94afd04d014a928b0da4d601bb2e97145811","